"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wjy1665702954149.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wjy1665702954149.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wjy1665702954149.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wjy1665702954149\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ODBC Configuration Utility\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__odbc_configuration_utility_163699\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__p_d55016e1_d55017e1_d55018e1\">Before you can use the ODBC Connector to make a connection to a data source, you must configure the assignment file with the specific settings appropriate for your data source.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__p_d55019e1_d55020e1_d55021e1\">Uniface supplies configuration utilities named <span class=\"ph filepath\">uodbccfg.exe</span> (for version U4.0) and <span class=\"ph filepath\">uodbccfg41.exe</span> (for version U4.1) to ease the task of configuring the assignment files. The outward appearance of the utilities is the same and they work the same way.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__p_d55022e1_d55023e1_d55024e1\">The configuration utility has the following functionality:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25352e1_d25353e1_d25354e1\">Connects to an ODBC data source of your choice\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25355e1_d25356e1_d25357e1\">Detects data types available for that data source\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25358e1_d25359e1_d25360e1\">Detects connector settings for the data source\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25361e1_d25362e1_d25363e1\">Builds and displays an <span class=\"ph filepath\">.asn</span> fragment with the appropriate connector settings\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25364e1_d25365e1_d25366e1\">Displays the data types\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__li_d25367e1_d25368e1_d25369e1\">Allows you to save the connector settings and data type settings\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjy1665702954149__p_d55025e1_d55026e1_d55027e1\">After you have finished using this utility, merge the assignment fragment into your assignment file and make any necessary changes to it. All ODBC connector options are described elsewhere in the ODBC connector documentation.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ODBC Configuration Utility Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ODBC Configuration Utility Before you can use the ODBC Connector to make a connection to a data source, you must configure the assignment file with the specific settings appropriate for your data source. Uniface supplies configuration utilities named uodbccfg.exe (for version U4.0) and uodbccfg41.exe (for version U4.1) to ease the task of configuring the assignment files. The outward appearance of the utilities is the same and they work the same way. The configuration utility has the following functionality: Connects to an ODBC data source of your choice Detects data types available for that data source Detects connector settings for the data source Builds and displays an .asn fragment with the appropriate connector settings Displays the data types Allows you to save the connector settings and data type settings After you have finished using this utility, merge the assignment fragment into your assignment file and make any necessary changes to it. All ODBC connector options are described elsewhere in the ODBC connector documentation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}